update_wrf_bc:

File list:

Makefile
module_couple_uv.F
module_netcdf_interface.F
update_wrf_bc.F


Note: Only DEC and IBM compiler options in Makefile.
      You need manually change the compiler option
      in Makefile.


Files needed:

wrf_3dvar_output        Updated WRF IC (3DVAR analysis)
wrfbdy_d01              Original WRF BC

------------------------------------------------------------------
NOTE:

Keep an your own wrfinput_d01, it won't be used.
Keep an extra copy of wrfbdy_d01, it will be overwritten.

After run "update_wrf_bc", rename wrf_3dvar_output as wrfinput_d01

------------------------------------------------------------------

Compile:

	make

	(make clean to remove objs and execs)

	(Before compile, make sure you have proper paths to NETCDF.)

Run:

	update_wrf_bc

	(make sure you have all three files mentioned above)

------------------------------------------------------------------

Remember to rename wrf_3dvar_output as wrfinput_d01 before
you run WRF.

